{
  "id": "69f9a9643838d8d5a2799544",
  "title": "個人用のpinもどき",
  "created": 1777969533,
  "updated": 1777970564,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f9a9643838d8d5a2799544",
      "text": "個人用のpinもどき",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969533,
      "updated": 1777969533
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97b00000000003865d7",
      "text": "[アイコンの民主化]と[アイコンフィルター]を使って個人用のpinもどきを作るよ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969533,
      "updated": 1777969576
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865d9",
      "text": "まず、pin用のアイコン（ページ）をつくる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865da",
      "text": "ページ名はなんでもいいが、どういう目的なのか分かりやすいものがよい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865db",
      "text": "例えば、[suto3のpin]というように",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969556
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865de",
      "text": "次に、pinをしたいページに`[suto3のpin.icon]`を貼っていく",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865df",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9a97c00000000003865e0",
      "text": "そして、アイコンフィルターでフィルターにかける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777969534,
      "updated": 1777969534
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ac0c000000000068c32d",
      "text": "Add Filter → `suto3のpin` で`[suto3のpin.icon]`のアイコンのページのみが表示される",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970191,
      "updated": 1777970299
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9abd0000000000068c32a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a34d201b2b52b255ee6cce1aef9a1f63]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970130,
      "updated": 1777970131
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9abd1000000000068c32c",
      "text": "スクリーンショット",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970131,
      "updated": 1777970150
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9abd1000000000068c32b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970131,
      "updated": 1777970131
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ac7c000000000068c32e",
      "text": "pinを外す場合は`[suto3のpin.icon]`を消す",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970302,
      "updated": 1777970346
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ad01000000000068c331",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970436,
      "updated": 1777970436
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ac8a000000000068c32f",
      "text": "pinの数は制限はないが、検索の都合を考えて 100件以下に抑えたほうがよいと思う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970316,
      "updated": 1777970436
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ad07000000000068c332",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970442,
      "updated": 1777970442
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ad07000000000068c333",
      "text": "この方法でpinしたことは公開情報で、誰でも自由に閲覧できる点に注意",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970442,
      "updated": 1777970564
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9acb4000000000068c330",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777970359,
      "updated": 1777970359
    }
  ]
}